{"tid":849767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社福棍蔡海偉建議政府1校2社工  估計業界人手過剩可以應付","createTime":"2018-10-06T02:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T03:11:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4ab668a57eb211f16464d0a458f746d6ccfcc7","tid":849767,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T02:59:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421586-20181006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421586-20181006.htm&d=QiaWgH%2FHQ409H7xcLwSKa8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=63045671\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421586-20181006.htm&h=4733b33d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421586-20181006.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1421586_1_L_20181006101213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1421586_1_L_20181006101213.jpg&h=2e9c88dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校社會工作服務網絡副主席盧松標在一個電台節目指，調查顯示學校社工處理每個學生自殺個案，需要花33小時，但政府機制下社工平均只有13小時處理1宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n出席同一節目的社聯行政總裁蔡海偉，建議政府把1校1.2社工改為1校2社工，估計需要370個社工，政府資源和業界人手應該可以應付。<br />\n<br />\n港大社會工作及社會行政學系講座教授葉兆輝則希望，社會不要把整個學生精神健康責任放在社工上，如果能在學校動員成為學童守望者，會更加有效。"},{"pid":"ea5bd7c254a2cca85508421ec3576562e90d99fa","tid":849767,"uid":42393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:00:27.000Z","msg":"不如一校3社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ce139c01fd81c30b2a18d6add3502dfc763353","tid":849767,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"2020年: 一校3社工<br />\n<br />\n2025年: 一校5社工<br />\n<br />\n2030年: 一校10社工<br />\n<br />\n一味食殖民政府社福綜援<br />\n<br />\n對社會毫無貢獻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265279d8769a8074c715d987d4fb25c31181b524",